{"tid":1867350,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[唔敢罷工嘅入] 放工立即去九龍城行街","createTime":"2020-02-07T06:48:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-07T11:40:38.000Z","uid":187489,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"48c4a3336a43f618e33f187a6f3e62c9bf329ffc","tid":1867350,"uid":187489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T06:48:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">要人！！！！</span><br />\n<br />\n今日係deadline, 我地呢班唔敢罷工嘅垃圾，係咪連收工去聲援都懶得做？<br />\n<br />\n可以的話每人帶少少乾糧同水俾手足同自己(記得每幾個字就濕下喉嚨)<br />\n<br />\n保護好自己<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">今晚見</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[突發] 醫管局要人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1867080\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1867080</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"58335bc3cf5fcef86559a37fc7f9cf5f61e74091","tid":1867350,"uid":187489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T06:49:32.000Z","msg":"幫手推<br />\n今晚見"},{"pid":"4edc9ac3f1da767b74ee21106fad2ebb7dd62414","tid":1867350,"uid":187489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T06:54:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7551c79917cf2553789145fc9c86859dfaf1687a","tid":1867350,"uid":284932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T06:56:32.000Z","msg":"交通:<br />\n1. 搭黨鐵去旺角站<br />\n2. 行去先施/先達<br />\n3. 搭九巴 9 或 95 號<br />\n4. 醫院管理局大樓落車<br />\n<br />\n* 九龍東既巴絲可以搭九巴 1A, 在喇沙利道(聖德肋撒醫院)落車<br />\n* 旺角道人和門口架27號巴士都去到"},{"pid":"1dfd2416388ecd0d1ddeeef6de3011bc21561980","tid":1867350,"uid":187489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T06:58:32.000Z","msg":"【物資】（14:28）<br />\n❗️❗️現場物資已經足夠❗️❗️<br />\n請市民唔需要再送食物黎HAHO🙇🏻<br />\n- 有電風扇可以帶過去！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>「我本人僅此聲明，就算社區爆發，依然支持醫護繼續罷工，直至政府落實封關及其它訴求！」<br />\n<br />\n只要所有公民社會嘅個體都咁做，HAEA嘅人睇到，或者會回心轉意，堅持罷工到底</blockquote>"},{"pid":"eeb5c11318af46d7cd801b15f6c4ae98d2201a34","tid":1867350,"uid":126283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T07:01:48.000Z","msg":"要時刻留意身邊有冇曱甴扮人<br />\n尤其對面係曱甴屋"},{"pid":"f39cd84da4757cd70037f3953097feecea8bcf13","tid":1867350,"uid":187489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eeb5c11318af46d7cd801b15f6c4ae98d2201a34","tid":1867350,"uid":126283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T07:01:48.000Z","msg":"要時刻留意身邊有冇曱甴扮人<br />\n尤其對面係曱甴屋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T07:55:13.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n物資已足夠，要人"},{"pid":"32ceb7a3e5f0f83fc382aa3f943f1bd14e0d7116","tid":1867350,"uid":199838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T07:57:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c814ee6b3e688a73cc321465447853ef7486350c","tid":1867350,"uid":187489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7551c79917cf2553789145fc9c86859dfaf1687a","tid":1867350,"uid":284932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T06:56:32.000Z","msg":"交通:<br />\n1. 搭黨鐵去旺角站<br />\n2. 行去先施/先達<br />\n3. 搭九巴 9 或 95 號<br />\n4. 醫院管理局大樓落車<br />\n<br />\n* 九龍東既巴絲可以搭九巴 1A, 在喇沙利道(聖德肋撒醫院)落車<br />\n* 旺角道人和門口架27號巴士都去到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T08:10:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3264109dd35e3e508dbd90c2dc6f227d1713983f","tid":1867350,"uid":187489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T08:10:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4ed502f2f7db598d2da47abad2e9b96bc07cb788","tid":1867350,"uid":187489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T08:12:21.000Z","msg":"原來自己推好攰"},{"pid":"b6cbe603d69169a7d55a263efe42d7e537d92135","tid":1867350,"uid":235535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T08:13:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5a7961d173550522241946742afede2265770571","tid":1867350,"uid":51820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T08:13:28.000Z","msg":"推啊"},{"pi